  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 박스 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c113fd6b-4ac0-4400-bb0c-d19e1d58ea04\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c113fd6b-4ac0-4400-bb0c-d19e1d58ea04\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjM3/MDAxNzUzNTA3ODIyODU3.hFOr138tXTKIkq5-5i4PglMzAM-A-eGjKkQOYnFKW9Yg.HycfqomRcB8hspmpMaN-6uirRTEA98g9J5q5zxkczsEg.PNG/SE-c113fd6b-4ac0-4400-bb0c-d19e1d58ea04.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjM3/MDAxNzUzNTA3ODIyODU3.hFOr138tXTKIkq5-5i4PglMzAM-A-eGjKkQOYnFKW9Yg.HycfqomRcB8hspmpMaN-6uirRTEA98g9J5q5zxkczsEg.PNG/SE-c113fd6b-4ac0-4400-bb0c-d19e1d58ea04.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">서랍 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">용어는 100% 정의된 것은 아닙니다. 서랍 형태라고도 하고 S형 박스라고도 하며 슬리브나 슬라이드 모양이라는 표현도 사용합니다. 용어가 어떻든 간에 제작하는 방법은 크게 달라지게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08044c2d-df2c-4bfc-8c5a-7262758fe4ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15f2957a-42a3-4d36-9c1e-c779321d525e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-085f3a38-93db-4320-b96d-f11d9550c274\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a21451d9-f469-4205-81b0-a421cbfa3e6a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 서랍 형태의 박스는 싸바리로 튼튼하게 제작할 수도 있지만 비용이나 기간이 부담이라면 단상자 형태로 만들 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c140b5a8-feab-4d86-b979-dde3b376ebf6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:282px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c140b5a8-feab-4d86-b979-dde3b376ebf6\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjI5/MDAxNzUzNTEwMjk1ODYy.JL50oqb-SSJr19k4RPUgiTHHJpqpsUkcfAibZHjqH7Ag.zAug6XCQpEsANf5O9x3r0dDgL9et81IX7iNjty6Discg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8005.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"282\", \"originalHeight\" : \"175\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjI5/MDAxNzUzNTEwMjk1ODYy.JL50oqb-SSJr19k4RPUgiTHHJpqpsUkcfAibZHjqH7Ag.zAug6XCQpEsANf5O9x3r0dDgL9et81IX7iNjty6Discg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8005.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-73097134-2229-4b7d-aa28-e95d2c0c397d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37e0736d-7525-4ecf-a8d6-92b4e02db240\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5225e9d-aff1-4c4e-a4f6-59bef4144725\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지 형태는 통상 350g 이상의 두꺼운 종이로 전개도를 내려받아서 작업합니다. 직접 접어서 사용하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-625ee402-25f3-4825-8c6c-ede490e1bdd4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-625ee402-25f3-4825-8c6c-ede490e1bdd4\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjkw/MDAxNzUzNTEwNDQyNzQx.lvO8HgHDVeCmHYS7qDkbqyDdDN4T0dWa-sOv5kY8q18g.0KU86V_H4IYPC3s2V8SnoasMm5dfWkD-IXkowYGs-eYg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8006.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1771\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1163\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjkw/MDAxNzUzNTEwNDQyNzQx.lvO8HgHDVeCmHYS7qDkbqyDdDN4T0dWa-sOv5kY8q18g.0KU86V_H4IYPC3s2V8SnoasMm5dfWkD-IXkowYGs-eYg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8006.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5073878a-c86b-4316-a75b-9215be831788\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0cb7b77-4fb0-43c1-bccf-d2e3aef0d42a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumma