nk\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6acb145f-07ec-41cc-bcae-705d93bc4c6d\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjg0/MDAxNzUzNTEwODk5ODE1.Tm3V4F1p6JZ0EtduTNfOOEU2cLANvWjxSGrVxpMDYUgg.48imhEMXbfFGQr4K8JW_qoSMwvo_T64PyA6i_9Vgk3wg.PNG/SE-6acb145f-07ec-41cc-bcae-705d93bc4c6d.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjg0/MDAxNzUzNTEwODk5ODE1.Tm3V4F1p6JZ0EtduTNfOOEU2cLANvWjxSGrVxpMDYUgg.48imhEMXbfFGQr4K8JW_qoSMwvo_T64PyA6i_9Vgk3wg.PNG/SE-6acb145f-07ec-41cc-bcae-705d93bc4c6d.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-deb83f13-4e98-48eb-8cf9-4f9bc04ec203\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjY3/MDAxNzUzNTEwODg4Mjk3.dveiHiaTGyptteRSCwTOLztHyEyNORiUJ-JIeBdT7k0g.GamWbqaQa6syBXU3T3GkLWxLks-XQa6Q_AfLqc7__ncg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8008.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjY3/MDAxNzUzNTEwODg4Mjk3.dveiHiaTGyptteRSCwTOLztHyEyNORiUJ-JIeBdT7k0g.GamWbqaQa6syBXU3T3GkLWxLks-XQa6Q_AfLqc7__ncg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EB%B0%95%EC%8A%A4_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8008.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-280fdf34-7a9f-4e7f-bff2-b18ad5deb4d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c72f81f3-e825-4ef5-9988-32dee2a84d5a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b2abac5-bdbd-4373-a169-81c49c419c74\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 인쇄도 면지 등 외부/내부 어디든 가능하기 때문에 비용과 견적이 천차만별로 달라질 수 있습니다. 반드시 전문가와 상담을 통해 확인하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223947825328#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-90cbfb90-7ebd-4b05-9e30-d3844fcb2b45\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-39c21fd3-60f9-4098-9927-cc7d945d3596\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2122e962-268f-4e86-9c44-726001bbbb0e\" style=\"\">서랍 싸바리 구성</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c8dc340c-ee10-44a3-a5aa-c232d81e1adc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0dac8dc-9922-4985-a59c-a3865079cb9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-66c6578b-058a-4dde-b9fc-ff8a6daf763a\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>종이 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dea48658-3df8-4a23-b31b-9893208983ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-960a5c3d-abfa-456f-8e7b-a08502714ab6\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f67c521e-1e69-49bd-bac3-87bdbf4798a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2bf324ed-26bd-474f-a9d5-9be0cb88eb10\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸개지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-95040cae-c48d-467b-85f5-11e6556cde84\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 싸개지는 갱판지를 싸는 외부 종이를 말합니다. 120g 정도의 일반 종이를 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be5fabe4-33c7-488f-9f19-aa86300c7773\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e39aaa4-0303-415f-8a31-93b203caf43c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 종이는 일반 아트지나 스노우지, 모조지일 수도 있고 고급 수입용지나 펄지일 수도 있습니다. 또한 검은색의 밍크지 계열이나 색지로 합지가 가능하며 크라프트지나 특수 벨벳 용지도 다양하게 사용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-adb3843b-f0ee-4250-81b9-bb7790a3c7c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-584555b1-f9eb-4b69-baeb-8676ee9ad8ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bf5a68b0-475f-4f64-b2aa-aeebff564477\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dfd0e2f7-19d0-4a7a-b329-b7712309d75f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>갱판지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1b1b2e3-605c-4587-bf9e-e4b544c91ff7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 튼튼하게 골격을 만들어 주는 보루지의 일종입니다. 갱판지는 800g ~ 1400g까지 다양하지만 통상 1000g을 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-13043687-9752-49d4-8658-2e71ac0d65cd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c97398c7-f7f7-4816-ba99-bf59ca041975\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1f84f58-8d3a-478d-8feb-acff0e8afbbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e8672287-4690-447d-b060-0a600e38d0b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>면지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a9bca10-7548-4e25-8181-d22a447c4c44\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 외부의 싸개와는 별도로 내부를 감싸는 종이입니다. 면지에는 통상 인쇄를 진행하지 않지만 내부에 인쇄를 진행하는 경우 면지에 인쇄를 해서 합지할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af8e70a4-8868-4a73-a976-eca49ab3f29b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0706e140-4b3a-40c7-944f-c9ccfb7a3602\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69c00ba3-2da7-4b37-97e5-a27787e168eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ea197886-0406-4c0e-9193-a9199734f072\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b099adb3-637c-442f-bbdb-3c051653293b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e8905ee1-0516-4673-ba97-3e0ca0b0e414\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b286a8e8-c1d6-48ed-8ff3-d1becb0524d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96403a70-2176-42f7-9481-9e70155db782\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슬라이드 박스의 사이즈는 가로, 세로, 높이로 제작되며 겉지의 경우 내피보다 1~3mm 정도 크게 제작하여 작업됩니다. 너무 헐겁거나 안 끼워지는 일이 발생되지 않도록 경험 많은 패키지 회사와 거래하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a8d9ada-1d5b-4ffa-bece-f9e300584897\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-44a141bd-f854-459c-9a05-0e9eac9677f4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5df52a50-70c4-4f87-9c89-6a2ea1a8e3ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-35ce78c7-4d00-4f79-b7de-4eb28203beb2\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce2bd8b3-b3ee-47a5-a180-2617d042f863\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bcabcbf9-c987-4c8b-8a1a-6153961e81fe\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f1ec065-23c7-4a09-a4d1-453712c66b9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c21d405b-e253-46ab-aae3-d8ea5eaf8932\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본 4도 인쇄 외에 별색이나 베다 인쇄 또는 백색 인쇄 등으로 모든 인쇄 작업이 가능하다고 보시면 됩니다. 다만 인쇄가 추가될수록 비용은 상승합니다. 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e9bcd1cf-d340-43d2-8be2-66c3aff69440\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c91cbd3-43b4-4288-8d52-266201db7591\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c7eccb4-45aa-4e6b-aa63-57d6be01f85e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ab14b001-14a8-4ad2-a2d9-54c5a932cda9\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-651ca161-1834-480d-a308-3dc0ad94a2a7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cc7bd7a7-2347-4def-93da-f82eeab86dc8\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1be140e8-7a62-4355-ba3f-8190ea40ad9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b843c43f-2f87-41d6-9461-d0a0fcd7f4a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지에 들어가는 모든 후공정이 가능합니다. 박인쇄, 형압, 에폭시, 부분 실크 등 가능한 모든 후공정도 진행이 가능합니다. 다만 디자인 작업 시에 여러 가지 후공정 파일이나 칼선파일, 또는 실제 면지, 갱판지 등등의 데이터가 경험 없는 디자이너가 작업을 하게 되면 사고가 발생할 확률이 높아집니다. 반드시 전문 업체와 상의하시기를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fa0bf269-82c5-49fe-9498-13f06108ebf3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffe22476-81d8-4514-b302-3e273c7d73cc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-928747c9-8dfa-44cd-ac43-957ffa50b317\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1a7af026-675e-4fcc-95c2-93b2b0a1a926\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>합지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f973f352-94ae-49c5-869e-028ae1f725d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cd4df9d7-0df9-444f-9b5a-55ed0d8f00e7\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd86b3ff-5d36-4193-ab8b-6defec16a7be\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-567ac3a3-466e-4860-8cd4-faa20150e758\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지의 싸개지와 갱판지를 붙이는 작업을 합니다. 바람을 빼야 하고 하나하나 에러 없이 꼼꼼히 접착제를 붙여 작업을 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-fd179391-80d4-444e-a61d-b94a26574da4\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-eafecc4d-fce7-4225-8557-9cbe42b3f911\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b69a3df-01b9-4b64-8254-bc8314ee8a65\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-50b57234-3f60-4d8b-b66e-eaf7ec116740\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3886533-43db-4a09-bcc8-749e2534427c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-08d0dfc5-c0e1-4ab1-ad8d-01ab8e66c3f5\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-889a3347-632b-485d-9258-c0e1d50204f0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a969893-faa6-40bb-ab84-99f4d96614a2\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b23b0cfc-b0bc-4ef1-b456-a116aa5e076d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b5c7b3f-d697-4141-a52a-f02a1cd22367\" style=\"color:#555555;\">목형, 종이 패드, 조립, 포장 등 싸바리 작업은 손가는 작업이 많습니다. 패키지 하나하나의 단가가 비싸기 때문에 반드시 꼼꼼하게 하나씩 조립하여 납품할 수밖에 없습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4cf9416-e99a-4a90-8a04-e06c24d94939\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b4cf9416-e99a-4a90-8a04-e06c24d94939\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjMz/MDAxNzUzNTEyMzQ0NjUz.SMmV8-nhlZjuTIBWb-8A0KW_sXGOoaDNUi2f1gEHVg0g.jawRj_Gt5Fczzh2hgt3GKb1o8YGDKFO89paO1hhm3cog.JPEG/SE-b4cf9416-e99a-4a90-8a04-e06c24d94939.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2250\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2493\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MjZfMjMz/MDAxNzUzNTEyMzQ0NjUz.SMmV8-nhlZjuTIBWb-8A0KW_sXGOoaDNUi2f1gEHVg0g.jawRj_Gt5Fczzh2hgt3GKb1o8YGDKFO89paO1hhm3cog.JPEG/SE-b4cf9416-e99a-4a90-8a04-e06c24d94939.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a8b4dd32-22a1-469b-9237-6d76a40d56a6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ff72398-713e-4530-b5b9-42367612be19\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-46df2038-a41b-423a-9bf5-ddcf9b035f61\" style=\"\">이런 회사나 분은 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1fafaf84-869a-4885-954b-8ec5940cadab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62480809-213a-4f12-8e40-c5656047c869\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7c340d6-4098-4bbb-a725-ffae5d0f5fac\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">□ 고객 감사용 감사 패키지 박스를 최고급으로 만들고 싶으신 병원이나 회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e246e8b-3a32-4e58-9c67-ed401a15d5f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1795465-22de-4f45-afed-d13317e07ccf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0269dcd-f930-44a7-b0c1-d968018a13e5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a25d8f05-5fdd-43be-9b40-195ed33b8b58\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">□ 임직원 추석 선물세트에 특별한 의미를 부여하고 싶은 회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2fb0ffd-4d08-4fac-8f98-2d6c6c165563\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25e37c0c-ff25-4cb4-86cd-ff525a7664d3\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcd03e99-d73f-4ff0-ab1f-43c6fa5947d7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f56f4f30-a0fa-4b1